Eventful,is,the,world,s,largest,collection,of,events,taking,place,in,local,markets,throughout,the,world,from,concerts,and,sports,to,singles,events,and,political,rallies,Eventful,com,is,built,upon,a,unique,open,platform,that,enables,partners,and,web,applications,to,leverage,Eventful,s,data,features,and,functionality,via,the,Eventful,API,The,Eventful,API,provides,access,to,the,entire,site,database,enabling,developers,to,integrate,it,and,the,functionality,of,the,Eventful,platform,into,web,applications,Common,API,tasks,include,event,and,venue,search,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,either,XML,JSON,or,YAML